### Create Order
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
accept: application/json

{
    "product_name": "Pizza",
    "quantity": 3,
    "price": 80.9
}

### List Orders
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
accept: application/json

### Get Order
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders/1 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
accept: application/json

### Update Order
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders/1 HTTP/1.1
